        {
          "name": "GET effective scan policy for repo (inheritance chain)",
          "description": "Returns whichever policy actually applies. Look at inherited_from to know the source: \"repo\" (this repo has its own override), \"org\" (inheriting from org default), \"tenant\" (inheriting from tenant policy), \"default\" (no row anywhere — synthesised default).",
